544
00:29:23,309 --> 00:29:24,595
C'est la nature humaine.

545
00:29:24,974 --> 00:29:25,974
En effet.

546
00:29:27,229 --> 00:29:28,635
Voici l'idée, Patrick.

547
00:29:29,006 --> 00:29:31,143
