00:29:39,686 --> 00:29:40,764
Ou presque.

553
00:29:41,819 --> 00:29:43,026
Très correct.

554
00:29:43,406 --> 00:29:44,156
Fini ?

555
00:29:45,785 --> 00:29:47,750
